{"tid":1645504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夜晚千祈唔好獨自外出","createTime":"2019-10-11T02:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T07:52:20.000Z","uid":93479,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"511bdf9d6857539527d6cd3a5c1d83f16c2ec5d7","tid":1645504,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:07:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭要全港攬炒，棄經濟，棄治安，要將所有惡果歸咎於示威</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好似陳小朋友咁無啦啦畀人夾走, 我諗仲有好多單都生死未卜, 佢地未必個個都係示威者. 挾佢地既亦未必係黑警, 可以純係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>變態殺手</strong></span>, <br />\n<br />\n最近有幾單停車&gt;笠人&gt;開車，跟住無晒消息<br />\n畀警察拉到仲可能法庭見<br />\n如果有變態殺手組隊，著到黑警咁，專揀示威日子出沒，隨街見女就拖上車姦殺再拋落海<br />\n<br />\n途人唔敢埋去，黑警見到係後生又唔理(年青已經是原罪) ，以後響街啲女就慘<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>大家請同家人定時保持聯絡，香港已經變成夜晚不宜外出的地方</strong></span>"},{"pid":"10abb1d814ad16a1bb5a623d1cb062ede2a8ea44","tid":1645504,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:09:58.000Z","msg":"香港好危險"},{"pid":"6bb88c108ef2c5edbaf4ac034633d29a5bf04078","tid":1645504,"uid":266668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fb07ce95dcde0e8163f60f3e80df3a6db43789","tid":1645504,"uid":313356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:10:50.000Z","msg":"港人要治港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f1aab31f4fb5139b2650f76bc5e8a6194db809","tid":1645504,"uid":93479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"07fb07ce95dcde0e8163f60f3e80df3a6db43789","tid":1645504,"uid":313356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:10:50.000Z","msg":"港人要治港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:23:32.000Z","msg":"各區自衛隊講極都組唔到"},{"